<template>
    <router-view></router-view>

<script>
import { onMounted } from 'vue'
import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
export default {
  setup() {
    const route = useRoute()
    onMounted(() => {
      console.log(1, route.name) // just output undefined
      setTimeout(() => console.log(2, route.name), 1000) // 'Home'!
    })
  },
}
</script>
